    An implementation of the model object 'Concept'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Inactivation Indicator Ref Set Members
    • Association Ref Set Members
    • Concrete Domain Ref Set Members
    • Definition Status
    • Outbound Relationships
    • Descriptions
    • Exhaustive
    • Fully Specified Name
    • Primitive
